# Version 1: Non-NGINX Baseline Deployment

> **Baseline Node.js deployment demonstrating common anti-patterns for thesis comparison**

This deployment package represents **Version 1** of the Urine Disease Detection System, intentionally configured with realistic Node.js anti-patterns that cause performance bottlenecks. It serves as the baseline for thesis research, comparing against Version 2 (NGINX+PM2 optimized).

